'''乌语'''或'''濮满语'''是一种在[[中国|中国]]云南省[[双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县|双江县]]和[[缅甸|缅甸]]由40,000人使用的[[南亚语系|南亚语系]][[佤德昂语支|佤德昂语支]]语言。在中国乌语使用者被划为[[布朗族|布朗族]]。

==位置==
{{see also|布朗族#布朗族人口分布}}
乌语分布在云南省[[双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县|双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县]]和邻近几个县。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sealang.net/sala/archives/pdf8/svantesson1988u.pdf |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-06-02 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223005131/http://sealang.net/sala/archives/pdf8/svantesson1988u.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

*Wang & Chen(1981)记录了[[双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县|双江县]]大凤山乡碰拚的乌语。
*Zhou & Yan(1983)记录了[[双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县|双江县]]永革乡胖品的乌语。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=100393 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-03-14 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407102955/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=100393 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*Yan & Zhou (2012)记录了[[永德县|永德县]]甘塘和胖品的乌语。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=124591 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2015-01-31 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305042722/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=124591 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=124563 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2015-01-30 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305172214/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=124563 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*Svantesson(1991:67)记录了[[双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县|双江县]]沙河乡邦协的乌语。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=178409 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-04-04 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222172616/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=178409 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

乌语2种主要方言都分布在[[双江拉祜族佤族布朗族傣族自治县|双江县]]：一个是公弄(现属勐库镇)，一个是邦丙和大文乡忙嘎；大文方言和[[施甸县|施甸县]]方言可以互通(''双江县民族志'' 1995:160)。

Avala([[外名与内名|内名]]：''a21 va21 la21'')在云南省云县芒怀乡邦六使用。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=34085 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2021-02-22 |archive-date=2018-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817193355/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=34085 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2015. [https://zenodo.org/record/1127808 ''The Angkuic languages: a preliminary survey''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516193005/https://zenodo.org/record/1127808 |date=2020-05-16 }}. Paper presented ICAAL 6 (6th International Conference on Austroasiatic Linguistics), Siem Reap, Cambodia. {{doi|10.5281/zenodo.1127808}}</ref><ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2017. [https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/austroasiatic/avala Avala audio word list] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009124549/https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/austroasiatic/avala |date=2020-10-09 }}. Zenodo. {{doi|10.5281/zenodo.1123297}}</ref>

==音系==
乌语有4种声调：''高''、''低''、''升''、''降''，这从元音长度和韵尾特征发展而来。

